What you need to know:  Aubameyang was officially presented at Camp Nou after his signing was confirmed on Wednesday, the 32-year-old allowed to move on a free transfer after Arsenal terminated his contractHis deal at Barca runs until 2025 although there is a break clause in June 2023 and a buy-out clause set at 100 million eurosBarcelona will hope Aubameyang can help solve the team's scoring problems this season and make the difference in their fight to finish in La Liga's top four